 acoustic mode dampers. This paper explores the purposes behind these\nupgrades, and explains to the best of our knowledge the noise currently\nlimiting the sensitivity of each detector.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Aug 2020 03:20:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Aug 2020 16:39:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-15"}
