 hyperfine structure of the\n$^{225}$Ra$^+$ cation and $^{225}$RaF molecule. For the ground state of the\n$^{225}$RaF molecule, this contribution achieves 4\\%.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Aug 2020 13:31:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Sep 2020 15:41:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-18"}
